Flip the clip down and it doubles as a travel alarm clock. Store Policies Welcome to our eBay store! Payment • We accept payments via PayPal. • Please note that if you pay with an eBay e-check, we are not paid by PayPal for several days – until the e-check clears. • No checks, please. Returns We want satisfied customers and want you to shop with confidence with us. Therefore, please contact us FIRST if you have any issues. US Shipping Your purchase will be shipped quickly within 1-2 business after we receive your payment. Stated shipping costs are for the 48 states only. Please contact us prior to bidding for shipping costs to US addresses outside the 48 states (such as HI, AK, PR, etc), since UPS and USPS do charge more to ship to those addresses. Customer Service We are open Monday through Friday; 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM central time. We try to answer all questions within 1 business day or less. Please use the eBay message system when you send us a question as sometimes our spam filter may block your email. If you have a technical question on a product, please also visit the manufacturer web site - most have great sites that will answer your questions.
